other_tests.findings: Sinus rhythm at 8-bpm, LAD, LBBB, unchanged from prior.

Liver is normal in shape and contour with normal echogenicity. No focal hepatic lesions, main portal vein is patent, no intra- or extra-hepatic biliary duct dilation. Gallbladder is normal without wall edema or pericholecystic fluid, no cholelithiasis.
